Boyz II Men’s classic 1994 love song “I’ll Make Love to You” received a 2023 twist on the Valentine’s Day episode of “The Late Show.” “I’ll make love to you, or we can just watch YouTube and I’ll text you some memes while I’m next to you,” the group sang as altered lyrics in the comedy bit that aired Tuesday. Host Stephen Colbert then popped up dressed in white ― and with an earring ― to steal the show. Watch the video here: Compare it to the original here: